<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Coral Springs</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">The breathtaking lake also has a private beach as well as a 3-acre park that provides ample green spaces for the residents to enjoy their evening walks. </p>
            <p class="par-xl">Since the community is newly developed, the homes for sale in Coral Springs are designed in accordance with the needs and preferences of the contemporary home buyers and real estate investors.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">The community offers a myriad of housing options that primarily comprise single-family detached and attached units along with a few apartments and condominiums for the first time buyers available at an average price of $480,000.</p>
